To make an antDesign divider dark themed using CSS:

1. First, add the following class to your CSS file:

  ```
  .ant-divider-dark {
    background-color: #434343;
  }
  ```

2. Next, add the class "ant-divider-dark" to your Divider component:

  ```
  import { Divider } from 'antd';

  const MyComponent = () => {
    return (
      <div>
        <h1>My Component</h1>
        <Divider className="ant-divider-dark" />
        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit...</p>
      </div>
    );
  }
  ```

This will make the antDesign Divider component have a dark background color of #434343. You can adjust this color value to your desired shade of dark.

